            <title>1.0.18</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>Bug fixes</h3>
<ul>
<li>Sender names with quoted display names (e.g. <code>"Jim St. André"</code>) no longer show with stray backslashes around them in the thread view (BOX-14).</li>
</ul>]]></description>
