        <item>
            <title>1.0.16</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>What's new</h3>
<ul>
<li>⌘1 now jumps to your Inbox. With multiple accounts it selects All Inboxes; with a single account it selects that account's Inbox.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
